---
import SiteShell from '../../components/layout/SiteShell.astro';

const phone = '877-458-2557';
const digits = phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');
const phoneHref = `tel:+1${digits}`;
---

<SiteShell
  lang="en"
  title="FAQ"
  description="Common questions about ACA / Obamacare Marketplace plans."
  canonical="https://obamacarelocal.com/en/faq/"
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding:26px 0 14px">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="pill">Quick answers · Real help</span>
      <h1 style="margin:14px 0 10px">Frequently asked questions</h1>
      <p class="muted" style="max-width:70ch">If you don’t see your question here, call or text us and we’ll walk you through it.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:14px">
        <a class="btn btn-pill btn-gold" href={phoneHref}>Call / Text {phone}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:16px">
        <div class="card pad">
          <b>Do I qualify for a subsidy?</b>
          <p class="muted">Many families do. It depends on household size, estimated annual income, and access to affordable job-based coverage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pad">
          <b>What if my income changes?</b>
          <p class="muted">Update your Marketplace application as soon as possible to avoid surprises at tax time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pad">
          <b>Can I enroll outside Open Enrollment?</b>
          <p class="muted">Yes—if you qualify for a Special Enrollment Period (loss of coverage, move, marriage, newborn, etc.).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pad">
          <b>Will my doctors be in-network?</b>
          <p class="muted">Networks vary. When possible, we help you check doctors/hospitals before choosing a plan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pad">
          <b>Is “Obamacare” the same as Marketplace?</b>
          <p class="muted">In everyday language, yes. “Obamacare” commonly refers to ACA Marketplace coverage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pad">
          <b>Do you charge for help?</b>
          <p class="muted">In most cases, there’s no extra cost to you for using an agent. Ask us if you want the details.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card pad" style="margin-top:16px">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0;color:#0b1116">Ready to compare options?</h2>
        <p class="muted" style="margin:8px 0 0">
          Send us your ZIP code, household size, and estimated income. We’ll compare all available Marketplace plans and explain your best options.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top:14px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <a class="btn btn-pill btn-gold" href={phoneHref}>Call / Text {phone}</a>
          <a class="btn btn-pill btn-teal" href="/en/compare">Compare plans</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="muted" style="margin-top:14px;font-size:13px">
        Note: MLC Insurance is not affiliated with the government.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .section{padding:26px 0}
    h2{font-size:22px}
  </style>
</SiteShell>
